There's some moments like that.

00:30:44.000 --> 00:30:45.790 align:middle line:84%
But it was one of
the things in life,

00:30:45.790 --> 00:30:49.940 align:middle line:84%
if he-- Let's imagine
awareness like a flower.

00:30:49.940 --> 00:30:53.310 align:middle line:84%
When we're completely open,
and we, all of a sudden,

00:30:53.310 --> 00:30:55.800 align:middle line:84%
