you're going to get it,

00:31:53.160 --> 00:31:55.400 align:middle line:84%
but for sure you're
going to get it.

00:31:55.400 --> 00:31:58.680 align:middle line:84%
Because life will bring
many different events

00:31:58.680 --> 00:32:02.060 align:middle line:84%
