not exactly what you wanted.

00:32:06.970 --> 00:32:09.810 align:middle line:84%
Then you will take you for
what you really wanted.

00:32:09.810 --> 00:32:12.370 align:middle line:84%
That it-- but you need
to be fluid, instead

00:32:12.370 --> 00:32:14.290 align:middle line:90%
of having the resistance.

00:32:14.290 --> 00:32:18.350 align:middle line:84%
It-- that happen when you
master transformation.

00:32:18.350 --> 00:32:20.123 align:middle line:90%
You become that fluid.

00:32:20.123 --> 00:32:23.930 align:middle line:84%
You do an enormous amount
of travel, and in your life,

00:32:23.930 --> 00:32:27.460 align:middle line:84%
you have lineages that
