00:32:27.460 --> 00:32:31.930 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you have a wonderful
longevity in your family.

00:32:31.930 --> 00:32:34.910 align:middle line:84%
But you are still in a
vigorous travel schedule,

00:32:34.910 --> 00:32:39.310 align:middle line:84%
