00:32:43.940 --> 00:32:45.110 align:middle line:90%
I will ask you.

00:32:45.110 --> 00:32:47.380 align:middle line:90%
I don't even think about it.

00:32:47.380 --> 00:32:49.786 align:middle line:90%
It's just what I am.

00:32:49.786 --> 00:32:52.910 align:middle line:84%
I will-- I never would
think, oh, I will take things

00:32:52.910 --> 00:32:57.080 align:middle line:84%
personally or not, I
would take something

00:32:57.080 --> 00:32:58.830 align:middle line:90%
and going to make assumptions.

00:32:58.830 --> 00:33:01.290 align:middle line:84%
No, it's-- I'm
just whatever I am.

00:33:01.290 --> 00:33:02.470 align:middle line:84%
You know, many
people ask me, OK,

00:33:02.470 --> 00:33:04.810 align:middle line:90%
Miguel, what is what you are?

00:33:04.810 --> 00:33:09.160 align:middle line:84%
And I can use knowledge in
