00:33:09.160 --> 00:33:11.090 align:middle line:90%
But it will be a lie.

00:33:11.090 --> 00:33:14.090 align:middle line:84%
Because the truth is that
I have no idea what I am.

00:33:14.090 --> 00:33:17.970 align:middle line:84%
I don't know what I am, and it's
not relevant to know what I am.

00:33:17.970 --> 00:33:19.610 align:middle line:84%
You could almost
say that my identity

00:33:19.610 --> 00:33:23.200 align:middle line:84%
as an empty definition who's
subject to my own agreement.

00:33:23.200 --> 00:33:24.690 align:middle line:90%
Whatever I say yes.

00:33:24.690 --> 00:33:27.050 align:middle line:84%
Because an identity would be
an attachment to who you are,

00:33:27.050 --> 00:33:27.950 align:middle line:90%
right?

00:33:27.950 --> 00:33:28.880 align:middle line:90%
And that's the thing.

00:33:28.880 --> 00:33:32.290 align:middle line:84%
If I'm completely aware
that I'm the one saying yes,

00:33:32.290 --> 00:33:34.770 align:middle line:84%
that it's my agreement,
