00:33:34.770 --> 00:33:35.470 align:middle line:90%
I can say, no.

00:33:35.470 --> 00:33:36.830 align:middle line:90%
I can change it.

00:33:36.830 --> 00:33:39.640 align:middle line:84%
You can say-- let's use the
example of The Four Agreements

00:33:39.640 --> 00:33:41.610 align:middle line:84%
as the four conditions,
the way I was talking about

00:33:41.610 --> 00:33:43.670 align:middle line:90%
earlier, when I was growing up.

00:33:43.670 --> 00:33:45.880 align:middle line:84%
How do I detach
myself from that?

