totally different way.

00:34:12.540 --> 00:34:14.260 align:middle line:84%
Transformation, from
the point of view,

00:34:14.260 --> 00:34:16.650 align:middle line:84%
I accept myself for who I
am, at this very moment,

00:34:16.650 --> 00:34:19.040 align:middle line:90%
attachment and all.

00:34:19.040 --> 00:34:20.860 align:middle line:84%
I attach my-- I
