00:34:26.510 --> 00:34:29.900 align:middle line:84%
I accept that I'm
not doing my best.

00:34:29.900 --> 00:34:31.960 align:middle line:84%
This is who I am at
this very moment.

00:34:31.960 --> 00:34:33.570 align:middle line:90%
This is who I am.

00:34:33.570 --> 00:34:36.190 align:middle line:84%
At this very moment,
I can make a choice.

00:34:36.190 --> 00:34:42.139 align:middle line:84%
I can continue to do this, and
be at this level of attachment,

00:34:42.139 --> 00:34:44.199 align:middle line:84%
or I could say, I'm
going to change.

00:34:44.199 --> 00:34:48.170 align:middle line:84%
Not because I have to,
