00:34:52.030 --> 00:34:54.400 align:middle line:90%
and are in that place?

00:34:54.400 --> 00:34:56.330 align:middle line:84%
Well, that's actually
a very great thing

00:34:56.330 --> 00:34:59.120 align:middle line:84%
because one of the realizations
about transformation,

00:34:59.120 --> 00:35:03.370 align:middle line:84%
at least from my point of view,
