00:35:03.370 --> 00:35:05.690 align:middle line:90%
I'm only responsible for myself.

00:35:05.690 --> 00:35:09.330 align:middle line:84%
The power over anyone
ends at the fingertip

00:35:09.330 --> 00:35:11.240 align:middle line:90%
of my-- of my finger.

00:35:11.240 --> 00:35:12.940 align:middle line:90%
I have no power over my dad.

00:35:12.940 --> 00:35:14.140 align:middle line:90%
I have no power over you.

00:35:14.140 --> 00:35:16.390 align:middle line:84%
I don't even have
power over anyone.

00:35:16.390 --> 00:35:18.360 align:middle line:84%
The thing about it is
that, at that moment,

00:35:18.360 --> 00:35:21.740 align:middle line:84%
I realized that the only person
I am really responsible for

00:35:21.740 --> 00:35:23.320 align:middle line:90%
