00:35:47.460 --> 00:35:53.040 align:middle line:84%
full responsibility and take
on the power that is me,

00:35:53.040 --> 00:35:54.650 align:middle line:90%
my intent.

00:35:54.650 --> 00:35:57.160 align:middle line:84%
When I decide to
transform, when I

00:35:57.160 --> 00:36:01.440 align:middle line:84%
decide to let go
of an attachment,

00:36:01.440 --> 00:36:04.290 align:middle line:84%
I break the cycle
of domestication.

00:36:04.290 --> 00:36:07.110 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden,
I do things because I

00:36:07.110 --> 00:36:11.250 align:middle line:84%
recognize that my yes is
what is driving me to create.

00:36:11.250 --> 00:36:13.910 align:middle line:90%
My intent, my free will.

00:36:13.910 --> 00:36:17.910 align:middle line:84%
And when I say no, it's
because I want to say no.

00:36:17.910 --> 00:36:21.900 align:middle line:84%
And I accept myself, both
the good, I accept the bad.

00:36:21.900 --> 00:36:23.060 align:middle line:90%
I accept the ugly.

00:36:23.060 --> 00:36:27.290 align:middle line:84%
I accept myself as perfect,
because I am a life, not

00:36:27.290 --> 00:36:30.470 align:middle line:84%
because I'm perfect,
according to the judge,

00:36:30.470 --> 00:36:32.820 align:middle line:90%
or what I'm supposed to be.

00:36:32.820 --> 00:36:34.650 align:middle line:84%
I'm simply perfect
because I'm alive,

00:36:34.650 --> 00:36:39.560 align:middle line:84%
and as long as I'm alive,
I can evolve and change.

00:36:39.560 --> 00:36:43.000 align:middle line:84%
Because life evolves and
changes continuously.

