We can say that it looks
like the figure of Christ,

00:44:11.490 --> 00:44:14.010 align:middle line:84%
because we're familiar
with that figure,

00:44:14.010 --> 00:44:16.440 align:middle line:84%
so project that image
onto that, because that's

00:44:16.440 --> 00:44:17.300 align:middle line:90%
what we recognize.

00:44:17.300 --> 00:44:21.440 align:middle line:84%
Especially if we grew up with
that beautiful tradition.

00:44:21.440 --> 00:44:23.190 align:middle line:84%
And it's meant to
represent almost

00:44:23.190 --> 00:44:24.650 align:middle line:84%
the same thing,
which is basically,

00:44:24.650 --> 00:44:27.655 align:middle line:84%
that moment of
ascension, of divinity.

00:44:27.655 --> 00:44:30.610 align:middle line:84%
And for us, in our
tradition, is that moment

00:44:30.610 --> 00:44:32.680 align:middle line:90%
where we become alive.

00:44:32.680 --> 00:44:38.330 align:middle line:84%
That we're completely aware
that I am in control of my yes.

