00:46:05.090 --> 00:46:07.700 align:middle line:90%
and the beginning of the 1900s.

00:46:07.700 --> 00:46:10.660 align:middle line:84%
Something that was
relevant in their own life.

00:46:10.660 --> 00:46:13.830 align:middle line:84%
Don [INAUDIBLE],
which is his son,

00:46:13.830 --> 00:46:15.640 align:middle line:84%
teach-- taught it
in his own way.

00:46:15.640 --> 00:46:17.600 align:middle line:84%
When my grandmother
began to teach it,

00:46:17.600 --> 00:46:20.950 align:middle line:84%
it was dramatically different
from that of Don Ezekiel.

00:46:20.950 --> 00:46:23.120 align:middle line:84%
And by the time my
dad grabbed it, it

00:46:23.120 --> 00:46:25.160 align:middle line:90%
was incredibly different, one.

00:46:25.160 --> 00:46:28.280 align:middle line:84%
Because it's in English,
but also because he's

00:46:28.280 --> 00:46:30.180 align:middle line:84%
speaking to a whole
different audience.

00:46:30.180 --> 00:46:32.470 align:middle line:84%
And when me and my
brother teacher it,

00:46:32.470 --> 00:46:34.740 align:middle line:84%
it's even dramatically
different from me

00:46:34.740 --> 00:46:37.234 align:middle line:84%
and Jose, because we all
interpret it different.

00:46:37.234 --> 00:46:38.200 align:middle line:90%
That's how it's passed down.

00:46:38.200 --> 00:46:42.430 align:middle line:84%
The reason why is because, at
the essence of the tradition,

00:46:42.430 --> 00:46:45.740 align:middle line:90%
there's a lesson of life.

00:46:45.740 --> 00:46:49.040 align:middle line:84%
It's a combination
of life teaching us,

00:46:49.040 --> 00:46:51.950 align:middle line:84%
and there's the
teachings that allows

00:46:51.950 --> 00:46:55.210 align:middle line:90%
us to function in that world.

00:46:55.210 --> 00:46:56.890 align:middle line:90%
Yet life will still approach us.

00:46:56.890 --> 00:46:59.570 align:middle line:84%
As for example, the
story of "The Five Levels

00:46:59.570 --> 00:47:03.550 align:middle line:84%
of Attachment", if I put it
my-- in the old Toltec language,

00:47:03.550 --> 00:47:07.140 align:middle line:84%
it is the story of Tezcatlipoca,
the Smoking Mirror.

00:47:07.140 --> 00:47:11.120 align:middle line:84%
If I use the example
of the question of,

00:47:11.120 --> 00:47:13.060 align:middle line:84%
as I increase my
level of attachment

00:47:13.060 --> 00:47:16.270 align:middle line:84%
to a point where I can't see
anything but the illusion,

00:47:16.270 --> 00:47:20.090 align:middle line:84%
but my attachment, in the
story of Tezcatlipoca,

00:47:20.090 --> 00:47:25.360 align:middle line:84%
