a mirror in front of me.

00:47:34.160 --> 00:47:38.110 align:middle line:84%
Because that's what Tezcatlipoca
is, the Smoking Mirror.

00:47:38.110 --> 00:47:41.850 align:middle line:84%
It's the reflection
that I can't see,

00:47:41.850 --> 00:47:46.350 align:middle line:84%
because I have all this
distortion around me.

00:47:46.350 --> 00:47:49.980 align:middle line:84%
To break through the
smoke, I create doubt.

00:47:49.980 --> 00:47:51.870 align:middle line:84%
Be skeptical, but
learn to listen.

