00:48:27.920 --> 00:48:30.710 align:middle line:84%
I begin to become
aware that I am life,

00:48:30.710 --> 00:48:32.790 align:middle line:90%
and that's reflecting me.

00:48:32.790 --> 00:48:37.820 align:middle line:84%
At Level Two, I become aware
of the surface of the mirror,

00:48:37.820 --> 00:48:43.450 align:middle line:84%
