00:51:43.820 --> 00:51:45.480 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:51:45.480 --> 00:51:46.700 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:51:46.700 --> 00:51:49.980 align:middle line:84%
Your child doesn't
know how to speak,

00:51:49.980 --> 00:51:55.860 align:middle line:84%
but he has that presence, that
just his presence awake in you,

00:51:55.860 --> 00:52:00.540 align:middle line:84%
what you need to do to
communicate with your child.

00:52:00.540 --> 00:52:01.700 align:middle line:90%
And they can get it.

00:52:01.700 --> 00:52:03.110 align:middle line:90%
They get it completely.

00:52:03.110 --> 00:52:06.700 align:middle line:84%
An example is like, my son,
he's high-functioning autistic.

00:52:06.700 --> 00:52:08.860 align:middle line:90%
He's a-- he doesn't speak much.

00:52:08.860 --> 00:52:13.080 align:middle line:84%
He's verbally-- His verbal
skills are very, very minimal.

00:52:13.080 --> 00:52:15.890 align:middle line:84%
Yet, him and I
interact all the time.

00:52:15.890 --> 00:52:17.380 align:middle line:90%
He lets me know what he needs.

00:52:17.380 --> 00:52:18.370 align:middle line:90%
I can imagine, yeah.

00:52:18.370 --> 00:52:20.800 align:middle line:84%
And you know,
the thing is, when

00:52:20.800 --> 00:52:23.620 align:middle line:84%
I found out about his
condition, at first

00:52:23.620 --> 00:52:25.040 align:middle line:90%
I was totally mourning.

00:52:25.040 --> 00:52:28.390 align:middle line:84%
I was so sad, I
was so heartbroken.

00:52:28.390 --> 00:52:29.860 align:middle line:84%
And then, as I'm
watching him, and he

00:52:29.860 --> 00:52:34.260 align:middle line:84%
