then I'm like, what am I doing?

00:52:34.260 --> 00:52:38.430 align:middle line:84%
What am I being so
sad, and mourning

00:52:38.430 --> 00:52:40.320 align:middle line:90%
my son-- as if I lost my son?

00:52:40.320 --> 00:52:42.360 align:middle line:84%
And then I realized,
I lost the image

00:52:42.360 --> 00:52:44.620 align:middle line:90%
I was projecting onto him.

00:52:44.620 --> 00:52:47.020 align:middle line:84%
But the beautiful moment
is that I allowed myself

00:52:47.020 --> 00:52:49.060 align:middle line:84%
the opportunity to
see him for who he is,

00:52:49.060 --> 00:52:51.090 align:middle line:90%
and here he is smiling at me.

00:52:51.090 --> 00:52:53.520 align:middle line:84%
There's no language,
but he's smiling

00:52:53.520 --> 00:52:56.900 align:middle line:84%
at me with those beautiful
eyes, and it says, Daddy.

00:52:56.900 --> 00:52:59.300 align:middle line:84%
I have everything I need.
Ah, yes.

00:52:59.300 --> 00:53:00.320 align:middle line:90%
I don't need anything.

00:53:00.320 --> 00:53:01.080 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:53:01.080 --> 00:53:03.090 align:middle line:84%
And basically I'm
still domesticating

00:53:03.090 --> 00:53:06.360 align:middle line:84%
my child, because I'm
helping him engage the world,

00:53:06.360 --> 00:53:07.540 align:middle line:90%
and I'm pushing.

00:53:07.540 --> 00:53:09.810 align:middle line:84%
And it's different
than my little girl,

00:53:09.810 --> 00:53:13.430 align:middle line:84%
because my little girl doesn't
have the same needs as my son.

00:53:13.430 --> 00:53:17.830 align:middle line:84%
But I'm the father to both,
and I will engage them both,

00:53:17.830 --> 00:53:20.910 align:middle line:84%
together and individual,
because they're

00:53:20.910 --> 00:53:24.220 align:middle line:84%
both individual human beings.
Just like you.

00:53:24.220 --> 00:53:25.360 align:middle line:90%
Just like my dad.

00:53:25.360 --> 00:53:26.540 align:middle line:90%
Just like anyone.

00:53:26.540 --> 00:53:29.300 align:middle line:84%
When I respect everyone's
individuality, that they're

00:53:29.300 --> 00:53:34.850 align:middle line:84%
masters of their own life,
then my ability to engage you

00:53:34.850 --> 00:53:36.335 align:middle line:90%
is by permission.

00:53:36.335 --> 00:53:38.220 align:middle line:84%
Like, I can't-- I
don't change any one.

00:53:38.220 --> 00:53:40.030 align:middle line:90%
I just say my words.

00:53:40.030 --> 00:53:42.410 align:middle line:84%
But if someone hears my words,
and they agreed with me,

00:53:42.410 --> 00:53:46.600 align:middle line:84%
they've given permission to the
words, not me, to the words,

00:53:46.600 --> 00:53:47.634 align:middle line:90%
to impact their life.

00:53:47.634 --> 00:53:49.000 align:middle line:84%
And they're going to
grab it, and they're

00:53:49.000 --> 00:53:50.140 align:middle line:90%
going to run with it.

00:53:50.140 --> 00:53:53.380 align:middle line:84%
Well, I-- I think that you
are teaching us a new way

00:53:53.380 --> 00:53:54.900 align:middle line:90%
of communication that way.

00:53:54.900 --> 00:53:59.820 align:middle line:84%
And the video that we saw with
you talking with your heart

00:53:59.820 --> 00:54:03.060 align:middle line:84%
to various people, and just
having your hand on your heart

00:54:03.060 --> 00:54:05.840 align:middle line:84%
is such a great way
of showing us how

00:54:05.840 --> 00:54:08.190 align:middle line:90%
it is possible to communicate.

00:54:08.190 --> 00:54:10.990 align:middle line:84%
And I think that's pretty much
the future of communication.

00:54:10.990 --> 00:54:14.270 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we've gone from
speaking, to cell phones,

00:54:14.270 --> 00:54:15.260 align:middle line:90%
to voice mail.

00:54:15.260 --> 00:54:17.730 align:middle line:84%
It's going to be
telepathic everything.

00:54:17.730 --> 00:54:20.500 align:middle line:84%
Telepathic voice mail,
telepathic email.

00:54:20.500 --> 00:54:23.940 align:middle line:84%
Because if we really understand
the language of the heart,

00:54:23.940 --> 00:54:25.850 align:middle line:90%
that's the only true language.

00:54:25.850 --> 00:54:29.630 align:middle line:84%
It's existed for thousands,
and thousands of years,

00:54:29.630 --> 00:54:31.590 align:middle line:90%
and will always exist.

00:54:31.590 --> 00:54:33.480 align:middle line:84%
It is truly the
language of the heart.

00:54:33.480 --> 00:54:36.250 align:middle line:90%
That's why I love your essence.

00:54:36.250 --> 00:54:39.200 align:middle line:84%
You come here with
your gratitude,

00:54:39.200 --> 00:54:43.510 align:middle line:84%
