00:55:06.810 --> 00:55:09.060 align:middle line:84%
It's all through that--
the language of the heart.

00:55:09.060 --> 00:55:11.540 align:middle line:84%
And to me, that's the
whole point of all our work.

00:55:11.540 --> 00:55:12.795 align:middle line:90%
It's about communication.

00:55:12.795 --> 00:55:15.080 align:middle line:84%
When I first started, I thought
